# Potsdam Aquatics maintenance

- Site content lives in **`data/*.yaml`** (not JSON). **`js/content.js`** loads it; **`js/lib/js-yaml.min.js`** is required (blocking script before deferred `content.js`).
- When you change data shape, file names, loader logic, or user-visible behavior, update **`docs/EDITING.md`** and **`docs/AI-CONTEXT.md`**, and adjust **`AGENTS.md`** if agent workflow changes.
- Follow instructions in **`AGENTS.md`** for the full “update docs” expectation.
